   <p><li> Bates Gill, "Russia, Israel Help Force Modernization," <I>Jane's Defence Weekly</I>, January 31, 1996, p. 54.
   <p><li> "China secures deal to build `Flanker' fighters," <I>Jane's Defence Weekly</I>, February 14, 1996, p. 12.
