<p><li>    David A. Fulghum, "'97 Bottom-Up Review to Spotlight Operations," <I>Aviation Week and Space Technology</I>, September 11, 1995, p. 25.
  <p><li>  Thrust vectoring involves deflecting engine exhaust with vanes or nozzles to enable far greater maneuverability; "Su-37 dogfights will be `10 times as effective,'" <I>Jane's Defence Weekly</I>, July 10, 1996, p. 11.
   <p><li> "Phalcon may fly over China," <I>Flight International</I>, November 1-7, 1995, p. 6.
<p><li>    Ari Egozi, "Israel presses Russia in bid to clear way for China AEW deal," <I>Flight International</I>, July 17-23, 1996, p. 13.
