<BR><BR>


<h2>About This Version</h2>
<P>This newest version of Indexicon features a number of improvements,
including greater speed, more sophisticated analysis, a larger primary
lexicon, and enhanced logic when handling personal names. More details are
included in the <a href="SPECSHT.HTM#NEW">Product Description</a>.


<h2>Pricing Information</h2>
<ul>
<li>Indexicon 2.5, for Microsoft Word 6.0, 7.0, and 97 for Windows is now
available!  Price: $129. <P>

<LI>Upgrades for registered users are available:
<ul>
<li>$29.95
</ul>
</ul>

