<BR>UPGRADES</H2> <hr> 
<h3>Indexicon 2.0 is <a href="ORDER.HTM">now shipping</A> with versions 
avaliable for either Microsoft &#174; Word for Windows or WordPerfect&#174 
for Windows </h3> This newest version of Indexicon 
features a number of improvements, 
including greater speed, partial document indexing, a more powerful 
index entry editor, recognition of personal and geographic names, as well 
as incremental indexing. </CENTER><p>
