<html>
<head>
<title>WebAnchor</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<img src="WEBANCH.GIF">
<hr>
<P>
<h3><em>Automatic online indexing of your word-processing or HTML documents, with
hyperlinks to key words, ideas, and phrases.</em></h3>
<p>
With the aid of WebAnchor software, any word processing document or online
document can now feature its own hypertext index.
<p>
Remarkably comprehensive, WebAnchor adds usability to all your
material, organizing documents and allowing for quick reference and
ease of access to information.
<p>
Once the WebAnchor software is installed, your documents can be organized
by an automatic three-step process:
<blockquote>
<h4>
<ol>
<li>WebAnchor <em>analyzes</em> the document.
<li>It then <em>inserts hypertext "anchors"</em> within the document.
<li>WebAnchor <em>indexes</em> your document - creating a complete
alphabetized page index.
</ol>
</h4>
</blockquote>
<b>That's it!</b>
<center>
<table border=1>
<tr>
<td>
<b>With keywords and phrases now<br>
<em>hyperlinked,</em> readers can easily
jump<br>from one related concept to another.</b>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</center>
<p>
<h3>WebAnchor Demonstrations</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="WEBANCHOR/DEMOS/VATICAN.HTM">Vatican II documents</a>
<li><a href="WEBANCHOR/DEMOS/GATT.HTM">GATT, the General Agreement on
Tariffs and Trade</a>
</ul>
<p>
<hr>
