<P ALIGN=CENTER>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Indexicon Demonstration</H1>


<Blockquote>This is a demostration of how Indexicon works.  The screen shots
are taken from Indexicon 2.0 for Microsoft Word 6.0.
<P>
All you need to do before running Indexicon is open the document you wish to
index.  You dont need to build any control lists or concordance files;
Indexicon doesnt create an index by searching for a particular word and
"tagging" every instance of that word.  Indexicon actually reads your
document and chooses what terms to index based on their context within a
paragraph.</blockquote>

