<h1><IMG SRC="ANCR.GIF" ALT="AnchorPage logo" align=LEFT> The Top
AnchorPage'd Web Sites</h1><CENTER><B>...See how other Webmasters are 
putting AnchorPage to work on their sites...</b></center><hr>
<p>
<img src="NEW_TINY.GIF" alt="New!">"<a 
href="http://freenet.msp.mn.us/org/gajda/home.htm"> St. 
Margaret Shelter Care Inc.</a> is an independent 
non- profit organization founded by a number of expatriates of the West 
African nation of Ghana who are living in the United States. St. Margaret 
Shelter is dedicated to assist the people of the rural Sandema District 
to meet a number of very critical needs, and gain increased self-sufficiency 
in health care, education, and economic development."  Check out the 
automatically indexed version of their statement of purpose and plan for 
implementation. 
<p> <img src="NEW_TINY.GIF" alt="New!">Wayne Cunningham, news editor for 
