<HEAD><TITLE>"Welfare Reform" Act</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<h2>The Personal Responsibility and Work Opportunity Reconciliation 
Act of 1996</h2>
<hr>
<h3><a href="WELFARE/HOME.HTM">Welfare Reform</a></h3>

One of the most controversial acts to come out of Congress in recent 
years, this act has been called both the "most significant step towards 
ending the welfare state in recent history" and "the cruelest bill ever to 
cross a president's desk."  Take a look and decide for yourself.
<p>
<ul>
<li>All views, Phrase, Concept, Abstract, and Table of Contents were 
selected.
<li>Abstract level was set at "2," Concept level was set at "4," and Phrase 
level was set at "4."
<li>The Default template was used.
<li>A customized lexicon was created and used for this project.
<li>Phrase Horizontal links were selected.
<li>Both a Phrase A-Z page and a Concept A-Z page were created.
</ul>
