</ul>
<pre>








</pre>
<A NAME="UPGRADE"><CENTER><H2>Pricing Options</H2></CENTER>
<HR>
<P>
<h3><FONT COLOR="red" SIZE=+1>Full Year of Upgrades</FONT></h3>
<UL type="circ">
<LI>If you buy EchoSearch for <b>$49.95*</b>, you are eligible for free online
upgrades for a full calendar year from the date of purchase.  This includes
<b>ALL</b> upgrades, major and minor.</LI>
</UL>
<p>
<H3><FONT COLOR="red" SIZE=+1>6 Months of Upgrades</FONT></H3>
<UL type="circ">
<LI>If you buy EchoSearch for <b>$29.95*</b>, you are eligible for free online
upgrades for a period of six months from the date of purchase.  This includes
<b>ALL</b> upgrades, major and minor.</LI></UL>
<p><b>* Add $5 for shipping and handling (US only).</b>
<H3><FONT COLOR="red" SIZE=+1>Site Licenses/Quantity
Discounts</font></h3>
For site licenses and/or quantity discounts, call our
sales staff at <b>1-800-896-4212</b>, extension <b>200</b>.<pre>


</pre>
<A NAME="ORDER"><CENTER><h2>How to Order a Registered Copy of
Echosearch</h2></CENTER> <HR> <P>
<p><b>See <A HREF="#UPGRADE">above</a> for pricing options.</b>
<p> Our sales staff is available to take your order between 8 a.m. and 5
p.m. (Central time).  Orders placed before 12 p.m. will be processed that
business day.  Orders placed after that time will be processed the next
business day.  You can contact us via any of the following.  Be sure to
have the information listed <A HREF="#NAME">below</A> ready when you order.
<p><ul type="circ">
<li>Phone - 1-800-896-4212 <P> <li>Fax - 612-896-5101 <P> <li>E-mail - <a
href="mailto:esorder@iconovex.com">esorder@iconovex.com</a> <P> <li>Mail -
<blockquote> The Iconovex Corporation<br> 7900 Xerxes Ave.<br> Suite 550<br>
Bloomington, MN 55431</BLOCKQUOTE> <p>
Once your order is complete, you will need to <A
HREF="#VALIDATE">validate</A> your copy of EchoSearch. <p> <li>Or you can
order from within the EchoSearch program itself! Just <ul type="circ"> <li> .
. . open EchoSearch <li> . . . click on <b>Help - Customer Support</b> <li> .
. . click on the <b>Comment</b> link. <li> . . . on the form, fill in your
name and e-mail address. <li> . . . in the "Comments" window, just tell us
that you'd like to order a copy of EchoSearch and include your phone number;
we'll call you. </ul> <p>
<li>If you have EchoSearch version <b>1.03 or later</b>, you can
convert your evaluation copy to a purchased unit with a simple
phone call!  Just <ul type="circ">
<li> . . . Call us at 1-800-943-0292 and give us your credit
card number.
<li> . . . We will modify our database to show that you now own
a purchased copy.
<li> . . . <A HREF="#VALIDATE">Validate</A> your copy.</ul>
<p><li><b>Direct electronic
 purchase will be
available soon.</b></ul></ul><p>
<center><A NAME="NAME"><b>INFORMATION WE NEED FROM
YOU:</b></center><p> Please be sure to have the following information
ready when you call or include it with any mail or fax correspondence:
 <ol>
 <li><b>Your serial number</b> (on the <b>Help  About</b> screen or the
 expiration message screen).
  <li>Your name, address, phone number, and company name (if applicable).
  <li>Your email address.
  <li>(Phone and U.S. Mail orders) Credit card number and expiration date
  (Visa, MasterCard, American Express).
  <li>The number of copies you wish to order.
  </ol>
  <p>
  <b>Note:</b> If you wish, you can include credit card information when
  ordering via Fax, though the information may not be secure.  If you
  choose to place your order through email, a member of our sales staff
  will call you to get the necessary credit card information.<pre>


  </pre>
<A NAME="VALIDATE"><CENTER><h2>How to Validate Your Copy of
EchoSearch</h2></center><hr><p>
 Once you have contacted us and your order has been processed, you will need
 to validate your copy of EchoSearch in order to reflect that it is no longer
 and evaluation copy.  To do this:
 <ol>
 <li>If necessary, open your Internet connection.
 <li>Open EchoSearch.
 <li>Choose <b>Help  How
 to order</b>. <li>Click <b>Validate</b>.
 <li>Fill in the Validation Key, given to you by our Sales staff.
 <li>Click <b>Yes</b>.
  <li>Wait until the online validation is done (this might take a few
 seconds). <li>If the validation was successful, you will need to reopen
 EchoSearch before the validation will become effective.</ol>
 <pre>

 </pre>
<A NAME="ONUPGRADE"><center><h2>How to Upgrade Your Copy of
EchoSearch</h2></center><hr><p>
<center><b>*** In order to upgrade from within EchoSearch, you must own a
<u>registered</u> copy of version 1.04 or higher ***</b><br>
<b>*** If you own a registered copy of version 1.03 or older, see <a
href="#OLD">below</a>.</b> </center>
 <ol> <li> Open EchoSearch. <li> If
necessary, open your Internet connection. <li> Choose <b>Help - How to
upgrade</b>. <li> When prompted, click <b>Yes</b>. <br>  EchoSearch will first
check to see if there is an upgrade available (this process may take awhile).
If there is, and if you are eligible for the upgrade, EchoSearch will display
the new version that is available and the file size (KB). <li> Click
<b>Yes</b> to continue with the upgrade process. <br>If you wish to cancel
the upgrade, click <b>No</b>. To view the new features of the upgrade click
<b>What's New?</b> <li> Type in or use the <b>Browse</b> button to indicate
the directory in which you wish to save the upgrade file. <li> In the file
chooser dialog, click <b>OK</b>. <li>Once the download is complete, you will
be prompted to install EchoSearch. Choose <b>Yes</b> to close EchoSearch and
run the setup program.</ol><p>
<A NAME="OLD"><h3>How to Upgrade EchoSearch Versions 1.03 or Older</H3>
<ol>
<li>Write down your serial number (go to <b>HelpAbout</b> to get serial
number).
<li>Download the non-expiring version (1.07) from our Web site.  You may
install version 1.07 over the top of your previous version if you want.
Continue to use version 1.07 as you had used the one previously. <li>At
your convenience, call our Sales staff at 1-800-896-4212 and tell them
your previous serial number.  Ask them to transfer your
serial number from your previous version to version 1.07.<p>
  <hr>
  <p>
