<HEAD>
<TITLE>EchoSearch System Requirements</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY background="SPOTS.GIF">
<center><h1>System Requirements</h1></center>
<hr>
<p>
If you are running a system other than Windows 95 or Windows NT, <a
href="PLATFORM.HTM">click here.</a>
<p>
 <UL>
If you are running <b>Windows&#160;95</b>, you will need:<br>
<ul type="disc">
<li> A 32-bit connection to the Internet<br>
(Some providers, like Prodigy, do not yet support 32-bit connections. If you
use another major service provider, please see <a
href="Connect.html">Connect.html</a>.) <li> 486 processor or better <li> 8 MB
RAM (16 MB recommended) <li> A 32-bit Web browser (Netscape Navigator 2.0 or
later, Internet Explorer 2.0 or later, etc.)<br></ul> <p> If you are running
<b>Windows&#160;NT</b>, you will need: <ul type="disc"> <li> A 32-bit
connection to the Internet<br> (Some providers, like Prodigy, do not yet
support 32-bit connections. If you use another major service provider, please
see <a href="Connect.html">Connect.html</a>.) <li> 486 processor or better</br>
<li> 16 MB RAM<br> <li> A 32-bit Web browser (Netscape Navigator 2.0 or
later, Internet Explorer 2.0 or later, etc.)<br></ul> </ul> <p> <hr>
<center><H3><IMG SRC="HOT.GIF" BORDER="0" HEIGHT="43"
WIDTH="79"><A HREF="ESDOWNLOAD.HTM">Download a non-expiring
evaluation copy of EchoSearch 1.07 for Windows 95 or Windows NT
here!</A></H3></center>
