<h2>Vatican II</h2>
<hr>
<a href="VATICAN/index.htm"><h3>Vatican II - The Vatican Council  
Documents</h3></a> <p>
Here, indexed together with WebAnchor, are three of the most significant 
documents
to come out of the Second Vatican Council (1962-1965).  They are:
<ul>
<li>The Declaration on the Relation of the Church to Non-Christian Religions
(Nostra aetate)
<li>The Dogmatic Constitution on Divine Revelation (Dei verbum)
<li>The Decree on Ecumenism (Unitatis Redintegratio)
</ul>
All three documents were run together with the following settings:
<ul>
<li>Selectivity set at level "2."
<li>The "Books" template was used.
</ul>
