<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>
<CENTER><B>Sample 1</B></CENTER></H1>

<blockquote>
<P>This set of sample indexes was created from document on oceanography
(3,507 words), indexed at <A HREF="#s1lev1">Level 1</A>, <A
HREF="#s1lev3"> Level 3</A>, and <A HREF="#s1lev5">Level 5</A>.
<A HREF="OCEAN.HTM">View original document.</A>
</blockquote>

