<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>
<CENTER><B>Sample 2</B></CENTER></H1>

<blockquote>

<P>These set of indexes was created from a document excerpt on
photography (6,658 words), indexed at <A HREF="#s2lev1">Level 1</A>, <A
HREF="#s2lev3"> Level 3</A>, and <A HREF="#s2lev5">Level 5</A>.
<A HREF="PHOTGRAP.HTM">View original document</A>.
</blockquote>

<BR><BR>

<h2><a name="s2lev1"></a><B>Level 1 Index</B></h2>
<P>Generated by Indexicon in approximately 2 minutes.  45 minutes editing the
final index. A 50-word lexicon was also used, which took about 45 minutes to
create.  <A HREF="PHOTGRAP.HTM">View original document</A>

<A NAME="E7E731"></A>
