<html>
<head><title>Downloading and Installation Instructions for EchoSearch</title>
</head>
<body background="SPOTS.GIF">

<center>
<h2>Download and Installation Instructions for EchoSearch </h2>
</center>
<hr>
<a name="95"><h3>Installing EchoSearch for Windows 95:</h3>
<p>
<ol>
<li>  Download the file "es107.exe" to an empty directory.
<li>  Click the Start button on the task bar..
<li>  From the pop-up menu, click Run.
<li>  In the text box, enter c:\{directory}\es107.exe (where {directory} is
 the directory to which you have downloaded the file "es107.exe") and
click OK.
 <li>  This will unpack the archived file and begin your installation process automatically.
<li>  IMPORTANT: You will be presented with a copy of the EchoSearch Evaluation License Agreement. Read the agreement and click Accept to continue with installation.
<li>  Follow the instructions on the screen.
<li>  Please review the README.TXT file for any last minute changes or updates to EchoSearch.
<li>  For information on using EchoSearch with Internet Service Providers, see
<A HREF="Connect.html">Connect.html</A>. </ol>
<p>
<a name="NT"><h3>Installing EchoSearch for Windows NT:</h3>
<p>
<ol>
<li>  Download the file "es107.exe" to an empty directory.
<li>  From the Program or File Manager, choose Run.
<li>  In the text box, enter c:\{directory}\es107.exe (where {directory} is
 the directory to which you have downloaded the file "es107.exe").
 <li> This will unpack the archived file and begin your installation process
 automatically.
<li>  IMPORTANT: You will be presented with a copy of the EchoSearch Evaluation License Agreement. Read the agreement and click Accept to continue with installation.
<li>  Follow the instructions on the screen.
<li>  Please review the README.TXT file for any last minute changes or updates to EchoSearch.
<li>  For information on using EchoSearch with Internet Service Providers,
see <A HREF="Connect.html">Connect.html</A>. </ol> <p>
<p>
<hr>
<center><H3><IMG SRC="HOT.GIF" BORDER="0" HEIGHT="43"
WIDTH="79">
<A HREF="ESDOWNLOAD.HTM">Download a non-expiring
evaluation copy of EchoSearch 1.07 for Windows 95 or Windows NT
here!</A></H3></center>
<hr><p>
<center><a href="echo.map"><img src="MENU.JPG" border=0 alt="Navigation Menu"
ISMAP></center><pre>

</pre>
