</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>`(4) RESALE- The duty--
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(A) to offer for resale at wholesale rates any telecommunications
service that the carrier provides at retail to subscribers who are not
telecommunications carriers; and
</UL></UL></UL><P>
</BODY></HTML>
</DOC>
