by inserting before the heading of section 201 the following new heading:
</UL><P>
<H2><EM>`PART I--COMMON CARRIER REGULATION'.</EM>
</H2><P>
<UL><P>(c) STYLISTIC CONSISTENCY- The Act is amended so that--
