and
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(B) advertise the availability of such services and the charges
therefor using media of general distribution.
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>`(2) DESIGNATION OF ELIGIBLE TELECOMMUNICATIONS CARRIERS- A State
