and exclusively in the business of providing---
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(A) telecommunications services;
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(B) information services;
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(C) other services or products subject to the jurisdiction
of the Federal Communications Commission; or
</UL></UL></UL><P>
